---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---
<Container>
<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row">
    <div class="row items-center py-5 md:pr-16 md:w-6/12 md:py-10">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left space-y-3 bg-lime">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium leading-none sm:text-6xl"></h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center py-5 md:w-8/12 md:py-10">
        <p class="text-xl font-normal leading-7 text-center md:text-left"></p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class=" flex-row  items-center my-6 p-14 rounded-[45px]">
    <div class="grid  md:grid-cols-6  sm:grid-cols-1 justify-items-center relative w-full border border-lime rounded-3xl ">
        <div class="p-10 md:p-10 col-span-4">
            <p class="items-center justify-center text-sm md:text-xl font-normal mb-4 ">"In a true and ideal democratic system, freedom of speech is recognised as an important element. For that, independent media is essential as media plays vital role in people’s daily lives. Therefore, our media should always try to enlighten and educate the general public, by covering world affairs as well as providing general information – particularly news related to Tibet. This social responsibility should be implemented in the most dedicated manner, and consistently for as long as the need exists. The formation of a press club is a very welcome measure in order to improve and better organise the Tibetan media. I offer my prayers for the growth of an exemplary Association of Tibetan Journalists."</p>
            <span class="text-lime text-base md:text-xl font-medium">His Holiness the 14th Dalai Lama<br/></span><span class="text-sm font-normal">November 1997 Dharamshala India</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-10 col-span-2 ">
            <img src="/pictures/hhdl.jpeg" alt="hhdl" class="rounded-2xl  md:h-auto sm:h-40">
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>
